saveChanges

public void saveChanges()
This method should be called when changes are made inside an object through its reference obtained from any of the get methods of this class. e.g, if getKeyInfo() call is made and then changes are made inside the keyInfo, this method should be called to reflect changes when getAsSoapElement() is called finally
